---
import InnerLayout from '../layouts/InnerLayout.astro';
---

<InnerLayout title="Terms &amp; Conditions — HNB Investment Bank">
  <style is:global>
    .legal-body { max-width: 820px; }
    .legal-body h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .legal-body h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; padding-top: 0; border-top: none; }
    .legal-body h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin: 1.25rem 0 0.5rem; }
    .legal-body p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .legal-body ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .legal-body ul li { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .legal-body strong { color: var(--ink); }
    .legal-a-inner { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 3rem; }
    .legal-a-inner .legal-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .legal-b-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
    .legal-toc { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; position: sticky; top: calc(56px + 1.5rem); }
    .legal-toc h4 { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--muted); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .legal-toc a { display: block; padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--ink-2); text-decoration: none; }
    .legal-toc a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .legal-toc a:hover { color: var(--primary); background: oklch(0.43 0.150 248 / 0.04); }
    .legal-b-body { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2.5rem; }
    .legal-b-body .legal-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .legal-c-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
    .legal-c-main { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2.5rem; }
    .legal-c-main .legal-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .legal-c-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; position: sticky; top: calc(56px + 1.5rem); }
    .legal-highlight-card { background: oklch(0.43 0.150 248 / 0.05); border: 1px solid oklch(0.43 0.150 248 / 0.15); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
    .legal-highlight-card h5 { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .legal-highlight-card p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .legal-contact-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
    .legal-contact-card h5 { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .legal-contact-card p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .legal-contact-card a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .legal-b-layout, .legal-c-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .legal-toc, .legal-c-sidebar { position: static; }
    }
  </style>

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">The terms governing use of HNB Investment Bank's website, client portal, and investment services.</p>
      <div class="page-header-meta">
        <span class="pill">Last Updated: 01 January 2025</span>
        <span class="pill">Effective: 01 January 2025</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="page-body">
    <div class="page-bg-map" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
         SECTION 1: FULL T&C TEXT
    ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
    <section class="section-host" data-section-id="tc-text" data-section-label="Terms Text">

      <!-- VARIANT A: Single column full text -->
      <div class="variant" data-variant="A" data-variant-label="Simple" data-default-variant>
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="legal-a-inner">
              <div class="legal-meta">Effective date: 01 January 2025. These terms supersede all previous versions.</div>
              <div class="legal-body">
                <h2>1. Definitions</h2>
                <p><strong>"HNB IB"</strong> means HNB Investment Bank Limited and its subsidiaries. <strong>"Services"</strong> means all investment banking, brokerage, fixed income, and fund management services offered by HNB IB. <strong>"Website"</strong> means hnbib.lk and all subdomains. <strong>"Client"</strong> means any individual or entity that has entered into an account agreement with HNB IB or any of its subsidiaries. <strong>"User"</strong> means any person accessing the Website.</p>
                <h2>2. Regulatory Status</h2>
                <p>HNB Investment Bank Limited is a licensed investment bank regulated by the Securities and Exchange Commission of Sri Lanka (SEC) under the Securities and Exchange Commission Act No. 36 of 1987. HNB Stockbrokers Limited holds a valid trading member licence on the Colombo Stock Exchange (CSE). HNB Securities Limited is licensed as a Primary Dealer in Government Securities by the Central Bank of Sri Lanka (CBSL) under Section 104 of the Monetary Law Act.</p>
                <h2>3. Website Use</h2>
                <p>Access to and use of this Website is subject to these Terms and Conditions and all applicable laws. By accessing this Website, you accept these terms without limitation or qualification. We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time by posting the updated version on our Website.</p>
                <h3>3.1 Permitted Use</h3>
                <p>The Website and its content may be used for lawful purposes only. You may not: (a) use the Website to transmit any unlawful, threatening, or defamatory content; (b) attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Website or its underlying systems; (c) use automated tools to scrape or harvest content from the Website without our prior written consent.</p>
                <h3>3.2 Intellectual Property</h3>
                <p>All content on this Website, including text, graphics, logos, and research publications, is the property of HNB IB or its licensors and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may print or download content for personal, non-commercial use only.</p>
                <h2>4. Investment Services — General Terms</h2>
                <p>Use of HNB IB's investment services is governed by separate Client Agreements executed at account opening. These Terms and Conditions apply to Website access and do not create any investment advisory, broking, or custodian relationship. Nothing on this Website constitutes investment advice.</p>
                <h3>4.1 Not Investment Advice</h3>
                <p>All information, research publications, market commentary, rate tables, and calculator tools on this Website are provided for informational purposes only. They do not constitute investment advice, a solicitation to buy or sell any security, or an offer to provide investment management services. Past performance of any investment is not a reliable indicator of future results.</p>
                <h3>4.2 Risk Disclosure</h3>
                <p>Investment in securities, government instruments, and venture capital involves risk, including the possible loss of principal. The value of investments may go up or down. HNB IB does not guarantee the return of capital or any particular rate of return. Clients should read all relevant offer documents and, where appropriate, take independent financial advice before investing.</p>
                <h2>5. Repo and Treasury Bill Services</h2>
                <p>Repurchase Agreement and Treasury Bill services are provided by HNB Securities Limited, a CBSL-licensed Primary Dealer. All transactions are subject to the specific terms set out in the Repo Master Agreement and/or T-Bill client agreement executed at account opening. Interest rates displayed on the Website are indicative and subject to change without notice. The actual rate applicable to any Repo or T-Bill purchase will be confirmed in writing at the time of transaction.</p>
                <h2>6. Brokerage Services</h2>
                <p>Equity brokerage services are provided by HNB Stockbrokers Limited under its CSE trading member licence. All trades are executed in accordance with the CSE Rules, Securities and Exchange Commission Act, and the terms of the Client Agreement. HNB Stockbrokers acts as agent and not as principal in equity transactions unless expressly stated otherwise.</p>
                <h2>7. Limitations of Liability</h2>
                <p>To the maximum extent permitted by Sri Lankan law, HNB IB shall not be liable for: (a) any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential loss arising from use of the Website; (b) any loss arising from investment decisions made in reliance on information published on the Website; (c) interruptions, delays, or failures in the operation of the Website or client systems; (d) any unauthorised access to or alteration of your transmissions or data.</p>
                <h2>8. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
                <p>These Terms and Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka. Any dispute arising under or in connection with these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Sri Lanka.</p>
                <h2>9. AML and Sanctions Compliance</h2>
                <p>HNB IB is committed to full compliance with Sri Lanka's Anti-Money Laundering and Counter-Terrorism Financing laws, including the Financial Transactions Reporting Act No. 6 of 2006 (FTRA), the Prevention of Money Laundering Act No. 5 of 2006 (PMLA), and the United Nations Regulations on Targeted Financial Sanctions. We will refuse to provide services to, or transact on behalf of, any person or entity that is the subject of applicable financial sanctions or who is unable to satisfy our KYC requirements.</p>
                <h2>10. Dispute Resolution</h2>
                <p>Clients with complaints regarding our services should first contact our Compliance Department at <a href="mailto:compliance@hnbib.lk">compliance@hnbib.lk</a>. If the matter is not resolved within 30 business days, clients may refer the matter to the SEC of Sri Lanka or, for Primary Dealer matters, to the CBSL.</p>
                <h2>11. Changes to These Terms</h2>
                <p>We may modify these Terms and Conditions at any time. Updates will be posted on this page with a revised effective date. Continued use of the Website constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
                <h2>12. Contact</h2>
                <p>For legal and compliance enquiries: <a href="mailto:compliance@hnbib.lk">compliance@hnbib.lk</a> · HNB Investment Bank Limited · 479, T B Jayah Mawatha, Colombo 10 · +94 11 250 0000</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /variant A -->

      <!-- VARIANT B: Two-col with TOC -->
      <div class="variant" data-variant="B" data-variant-label="Middle">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="legal-b-layout">
              <nav class="legal-toc" aria-label="T&C sections">
                <h4>Contents</h4>
                <a href="#tc-1">1. Definitions</a>
                <a href="#tc-2">2. Regulatory Status</a>
                <a href="#tc-3">3. Website Use</a>
                <a href="#tc-4">4. Investment Services</a>
                <a href="#tc-5">5. Repo &amp; T-Bill</a>
                <a href="#tc-6">6. Brokerage</a>
                <a href="#tc-7">7. Liability</a>
                <a href="#tc-8">8. Governing Law</a>
                <a href="#tc-9">9. AML &amp; Sanctions</a>
                <a href="#tc-10">10. Disputes</a>
                <a href="#tc-11">11. Changes</a>
              </nav>
              <div class="legal-b-body">
                <div class="legal-meta">Last updated: 01 January 2025</div>
                <div class="legal-body">
                  <h2 id="tc-1">1. Definitions</h2>
                  <p>"HNB IB" = HNB Investment Bank Limited and subsidiaries. "Services" = all investment banking services. "Website" = hnbib.lk. "Client" = account holder. "User" = any website visitor.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-2">2. Regulatory Status</h2>
                  <p>HNB Investment Bank: SEC-licensed investment bank. HNB Stockbrokers: CSE trading member. HNB Securities: CBSL Primary Dealer in Government Securities.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-3">3. Website Use</h2>
                  <p>Lawful use only. No scraping, no unauthorised access. All content is copyright HNB IB. Personal, non-commercial use permitted.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-4">4. Investment Services — Not Advice</h2>
                  <p>All website content is informational only. Not investment advice. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Risk of loss exists in all investments.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-5">5. Repo and T-Bill Services</h2>
                  <p>Provided by HNB Securities Limited (CBSL Primary Dealer). Rates are indicative. Actual rates confirmed in writing at transaction time per the executed Repo Master Agreement.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-6">6. Brokerage Services</h2>
                  <p>Provided by HNB Stockbrokers Limited (CSE member). HNB Stockbrokers acts as agent in equity transactions unless stated otherwise.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-7">7. Liability</h2>
                  <p>HNB IB's liability is excluded to the maximum extent permitted by Sri Lankan law for losses arising from Website use, investment decisions, system failures, or unauthorised access.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-8">8. Governing Law</h2>
                  <p>Laws of Sri Lanka. Exclusive jurisdiction of Sri Lankan courts.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-9">9. AML &amp; Sanctions</h2>
                  <p>Full compliance with FTRA, PMLA, and UN targeted financial sanctions. Services refused to sanctioned parties or those failing KYC.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-10">10. Disputes</h2>
                  <p>First contact Compliance: <a href="mailto:compliance@hnbib.lk">compliance@hnbib.lk</a>. If unresolved in 30 business days, refer to SEC or CBSL as applicable.</p>
                  <h2 id="tc-11">11. Changes</h2>
                  <p>Terms may be updated at any time. Continued use constitutes acceptance.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /variant B -->

      <!-- VARIANT C: With sidebar highlights -->
      <div class="variant" data-variant="C" data-variant-label="Ambitious">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="legal-c-layout">
              <div class="legal-c-main">
                <div class="legal-meta">Effective 01 January 2025 · Governed by laws of Sri Lanka</div>
                <div class="legal-body">
                  <h2>1. Who We Are &amp; Regulatory Status</h2>
                  <p>HNB Investment Bank Limited: SEC-licensed. HNB Stockbrokers Limited: CSE trading member. HNB Securities Limited: CBSL Primary Dealer. All registered at 479, T B Jayah Mawatha, Colombo 10.</p>
                  <h2>2. Website &amp; Content Use</h2>
                  <p>Lawful, personal, non-commercial use only. All content is protected by copyright. No scraping or automated harvesting without written consent. Use of the Website does not create any investment relationship.</p>
                  <h2>3. Not Investment Advice</h2>
                  <p>All information on this Website — including rates, research, market commentary, and calculator outputs — is for informational purposes only. It does not constitute investment advice or a solicitation. Investments carry risk of loss. Seek independent advice where appropriate.</p>
                  <h2>4. Service-Specific Terms</h2>
                  <p><strong>Repos / T-Bills:</strong> HNB Securities (CBSL Primary Dealer). Rates indicative only; confirmed in writing at transaction. Governed by Repo Master Agreement.</p>
                  <p><strong>Equity Brokerage:</strong> HNB Stockbrokers (CSE member). Agent only. Governed by Client Agreement and CSE Rules.</p>
                  <h2>5. Liability, Governing Law &amp; Disputes</h2>
                  <p>Liability excluded to maximum extent permitted by Sri Lankan law. Governed exclusively by Sri Lankan law. Complaints to <a href="mailto:compliance@hnbib.lk">compliance@hnbib.lk</a> first; escalate to SEC or CBSL after 30 business days.</p>
                  <h2>6. AML &amp; Sanctions</h2>
                  <p>Full compliance with FTRA, PMLA, and UN financial sanctions. Services refused to sanctioned parties. KYC mandatory for all clients.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="legal-c-sidebar">
                <div class="legal-highlight-card">
                  <h5>Key Point: Not Investment Advice</h5>
                  <p>Nothing on this website — including rates, research notes, calculator outputs, or market commentary — constitutes investment advice. Always verify with a qualified professional.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="legal-highlight-card">
                  <h5>Regulatory Oversight</h5>
                  <p>SEC of Sri Lanka regulates securities activities. CBSL regulates the Primary Dealer. Both have jurisdiction over client complaints.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="legal-contact-card">
                  <h5>Compliance Contact</h5>
                  <p><a href="mailto:compliance@hnbib.lk">compliance@hnbib.lk</a><br/>+94 11 250 0000</p>
                </div>
                <div class="legal-contact-card">
                  <h5>Related</h5>
                  <p><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a><br/>Updated 01 Jan 2025</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /variant C -->

    </section><!-- /tc-text -->

  </div><!-- /page-body -->
</InnerLayout>
